    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide funding for train companies to give train drivers a pay rise ",
        "additional_details": "Throughout the pandemic, train drivers worked hard and that should be considered by people of UK.\r\n\r\nWe believe train drivers are hard working individuals who deserve increased pay, and this goal can\u2019t be reached unless they get the support of the people along with the government. Some train drivers have struggled during and after the coronavirus, and some struggle to pay for expenses leaving them with the bare minimum.\r\n",
        "background": "The Government should provide funding for train drivers to get a pay rise. They haven't had a pay rise since 2019.",
